<div class="pb-24 md:pb-32 pt-6">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden p-6">
      <p
        class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-pretty text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-950 text-left"
      >
        Contacto de soporte
      </p>
      <p
        class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-pretty text-left text-base font-medium text-gray-600"
      >
        Si necesitas asistencia, no dudes en ponerte en contacto con nuestro
        equipo de soporte, que estará encantado de ayudarte.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-2 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
      <div
        class="overflow-hidden shadow-sm rounded-xl relative bg-white p-6 divide-y divide-gray-200"
      >
        <div class="pb-6">
          <h2 class="text-gray-900 font-bold text-lg">Convesar sobre ventas</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
            Si tienes alguna pregunta sobre nuestros productos o servicios,
            ponte en contacto con nuestro equipo de ventas.
          </p>

          <a href="" class="underline text-gray-900 font-semibold block mt-6"
            >arxatec.developers@gmail.com</a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="text-gray-900 font-bold text-lg">Soporte por chat</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
            Si tienes alguna pregunta sobre nuestros productos o servicios,
            ponte en contacto con nuestro equipo de ventas.
          </p>

          <a href="" class="underline text-gray-900 font-semibold block mt-6">
            Iniciar chat en vivo</a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="text-gray-900 font-bold text-lg">Llamanos</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
            Visita nuestro línea de lunes a viernes, 9:00AM - 18:00PM.
          </p>

          <a href="" class="underline text-gray-900 font-semibold block mt-6"
            >+51 967523180</a
          >
          <a href="" class="underline text-gray-900 font-semibold block mt-2"
            >+04 012112</a
          >
        </div>
        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="text-gray-900 font-bold text-lg">Nuestras oficionas</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
            Visita nuestras oficinas de lunes a viernes, 9:00AM - 18:00PM.
          </p>

          <a href="" class="underline text-gray-900 font-semibold block mt-6"
            >Torre Galena 234, Huancayo, Junín, Perú</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-full">
            <label for="name" class="block text-sm/6 font-medium text-gray-900"
              >Nombre</label
            >
            <div class="mt-2">
              <input
                type="text"
                name="name"
                id="name"
                class="block w-full rounded-md bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-base text-gray-900 outline outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-gray-300 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline focus:outline-2 focus:-outline-offset-2 focus:outline-blue-600 sm:text-sm/6"
                placeholder="Juan"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full">
            <label
              for="lastname"
              class="block text-sm/6 font-medium text-gray-900">Apellido</label
            >
            <div class="mt-2">
              <input
                type="text"
                name="lastname"
                id="lastname"
                class="block w-full rounded-md bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-base text-gray-900 outline outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-gray-300 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline focus:outline-2 focus:-outline-offset-2 focus:outline-blue-600 sm:text-sm/6"
                placeholder="Perez"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <label for="email" class="block text-sm/6 font-medium text-gray-900"
            >Correo electrónico</label
          >
          <div class="mt-2">
            <input
              type="email"
              name="email"
              id="email"
              class="block w-full rounded-md bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-base text-gray-900 outline outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-gray-300 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline focus:outline-2 focus:-outline-offset-2 focus:outline-blue-600 sm:text-sm/6"
              placeholder="you@example.com"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <label for="phone" class="block text-sm/6 font-medium text-gray-900"
            >Número de telefóno</label
          >
          <div class="mt-2">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="phone"
              id="phone"
              class="block w-full rounded-md bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-base text-gray-900 outline outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-gray-300 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline focus:outline-2 focus:-outline-offset-2 focus:outline-blue-600 sm:text-sm/6"
              placeholder="+00 000 000 000"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <label for="country" class="block text-sm/6 font-medium text-gray-900"
            >País</label
          >
          <div class="mt-2">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="country"
              id="country"
              class="block w-full rounded-md bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-base text-gray-900 outline outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-gray-300 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline focus:outline-2 focus:-outline-offset-2 focus:outline-blue-600 sm:text-sm/6"
              placeholder="Perú"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4">
          <label for="country" class="block text-sm/6 font-medium text-gray-900"
            >Asunto</label
          >
          <div class="mt-2">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="country"
              id="country"
              class="block w-full rounded-md bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-base text-gray-900 outline outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-gray-300 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline focus:outline-2 focus:-outline-offset-2 focus:outline-blue-600 sm:text-sm/6"
              placeholder="No puedo acceder a mi cuenta"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4">
          <label for="comment" class="block text-sm/6 font-medium text-gray-900"
            >Mensaje</label
          >
          <div class="mt-2">
            <textarea
              rows="4"
              name="comment"
              id="comment"
              class="block w-full rounded-md bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-base text-gray-900 outline outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-gray-300 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:outline focus:outline-2 focus:-outline-offset-2 focus:outline-blue-600 sm:text-sm/6"
            ></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm mt-4 text-gray-700">
          Si envias en mensaje aceptas nuestros
          <a href="" class="font-semibold underline">terminos y condiciones</a> y
          nuestros
          <a href="" class="font-semibold underline">politica de privacidad</a>.
        </p>

        <button
          class="rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-xs hover:bg-blue-500 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-blue-600 w-full mt-12"
        >
          Enviar
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
